#circuitbreakersg day 55
Last day of circuit breaker tomorrow.. i can’t wait for phase 2 to come😑

Sichuan day

DIY Otah buns
Otah from @9sseafood and delicious soft Buns from @noodleman678

So affordable!

@eng_kee_noodle_house’s Wonton and dumplings have played a big part of my daily meal during this circuit breaker🤤

This time decided to make 红油抄手 Sichuan spicy Wonton in red oil. Using Lao Gan Ma 老干妈 chilli oil.

Wonton soup
Stir-fry potatoes & pork slices
Stir-fry beansprouts
Sichuan Vegetables

#stayhome #jxeatshome
@accentuatedfoodco oh i got the handmade wonton from @eng_kee_noodle_house !! soup was cooked with ikan bilis 😅
i’m a fan of soup dumplings but let me just say those look like the ones i patronize at this famous restaurant in toa payoh!!! you got to teach me how to make them 👨🏻‍🍳
Wah the otah bun looks so good!👍👍
what a feast 😍 looks so delicious 🤤❤️
@thefoodadv aww thank you! stay safe this period! the otah buns are so affordable and easy to make!
Press on haha, it's coming soon 😊 the otah buns look v good btw!
Good morning Min 😋👍 so sedap this is ❤️
@fatspoting 🤤🤤 yes can’t wait!! stay safe this period ❤️
Love those wantons!! 🤤 AND YASSS I can’t wait for Phase 2 to cone toooo
@jammin_with_ramen thank you, u are so kind❤️
@jxeats ayyy I'm just speaking the truth :)
You have some delicious things going on here. Excited to see what you share next 🤙🏼🤙🏼
